Name: Dirt Bike Insanity
About the game: It's a racing game that takes you into the world of motocross - Dirt Bikes. Sit behind the handlebar and race against opponents on many specially prepared tracks located in the different sceneries. The game has both large outdoor and indoor areas to explore, tracks are filled with different sets of hills, bumps, ramps and turns.
